  "id": "RAW_648f3821",
  "title": "Gemini Embedding 2：我们的首个原生多模态嵌入模型",
  "url": "https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/models-and-research/gemini-models/gemini-embedding-2/",
  "date": "2026-03-10 16:14:55",
  "author": "Min Choi",
  "siteName": "The Keyword (blog.google) ",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <uni-article-speakable style=\"height: 55px; margin-bottom: 36px; display: block;\" page-title=\"Gemini Embedding 2: Our first natively multimodal embedding model\" listen-to-article=\"Listen to article\" data-date-modified=\"2026-03-10T16:14:55.090652+00:00\" data-tracking-ids=\"G-HGNBTNCHCQ,G-6NKTLKV14N\" data-voice-list=\"en.ioh-pngnat:Cyan,en.usb-pngnat:Lime\" data-script-src=\"https://www.gstatic.com/readaloud/player/web/api/js/api.js\" data-highlight-mode=\"word-over-paragraph\">\n   <!---->\n   <div id=\"uni-article-speakable\">\n    <!--?lit$298740027$-->\n    <span width=\"14px\"> \n     <svg width=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 0 66 66\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"uni-spinner uni-spinner--small\">\n      <circle class=\"loader-path\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"7\" cx=\"33\" cy=\"33\" r=\"25\"></circle>\n     </svg> \n    </span>\n   </div>\n  </uni-article-speakable>\n  <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini Embedding 2: Our first natively multimodal embedding model&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini Embedding 2: Our first natively multimodal embedding model&quot;\n         }\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 36px; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\">\n      <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px auto;max-width:726px;\">\n       <div class=\"rich-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.625;\">\n        <p data-block-key=\"og3u5\" class=\"drop-cap\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">Today we’re releasing Gemini Embedding 2, our first fully multimodal embedding model built on the Gemini architecture, in Public Preview via the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/embeddings\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background: transparent; color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\">Gemini API</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.cloud.google.com/vertex-ai/generative-ai/docs/models/gemini/embedding-2\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background: transparent; color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\">Vertex AI</a>.</p>\n        <p data-block-key=\"2ho9i\" style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">Expanding on our previous text-only foundation, Gemini Embedding 2 maps text, images, videos, audio and documents into a single, unified embedding space, and captures semantic intent across over 100 languages. This simplifies complex pipelines and enhances a wide variety of multimodal downstream tasks—from Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) and semantic search to sentiment analysis and data clustering.</p>\n        <h2 data-block-key=\"bv5an\" style=\"padding:24px 0px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.25px;font-size:36px;line-height:44px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;overflow-wrap:break-word;margin-right:initial;margin-left:initial;font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;hyphens:none;\">New modalities and flexible output dimensions</h2>\n        <p data-block-key=\"9emar\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">The model is based on Gemini and leverages its best-in-class multimodal understanding capabilities to create high-quality embeddings across:</p>\n        <ul style=\"padding-left: 0px; list-style-position: outside; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 20px;\">\n         <li data-block-key=\"ea3uu\" style=\"margin: 36px 0px 24px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 5px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.625;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Text:</span>&nbsp;supports an expansive context of up to 8192 input tokens</li>\n         <li data-block-key=\"30en5\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 5px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.625;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Images:</span>&nbsp;capable of processing up to 6 images per request, supporting PNG and JPEG formats</li>\n         <li data-block-key=\"2sg68\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 5px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.625;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Videos:</span>&nbsp;supports up to 120 seconds of video input in MP4 and MOV formats</li>\n         <li data-block-key=\"6jtsl\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 5px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.625;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Audio:</span>&nbsp;natively ingests and embeds audio data without needing intermediate text transcriptions</li>\n         <li data-block-key=\"85l28\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 36px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 5px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.625;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Documents:</span>&nbsp;directly embed PDFs up to 6 pages long</li>\n        </ul>\n        <p data-block-key=\"cg3po\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">Beyond processing one modality at a time, this model natively understands interleaved input so you can pass multiple modalities of input (e.g., image + text) in a single request. This allows the model to capture the complex, nuanced relationships between different media types, unlocking more accurate understanding of complex, real-world data.</p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini Embedding 2: Our first natively multimodal embedding model&quot;}\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:726px;margin-inline:auto;margin-block-end:80px;\">\n      <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset image-full-width__media-asset--mp4 \" style=\"border-radius:8px;padding:0px;margin:0px;overflow:visible;aspect-ratio:auto;max-width:100%;width:726px;margin-inline:auto;height:auto;\">\n       <uni-video-player muted playsinline=\"\" controls=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" alt-text=\"Gemini 2 multimodal embeddings\" autoplay=\"\" video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/gemini-2-multimodal-embeddings.mp4\" tts-json=\"\" audio-descripted-video=\"\" section-header=\"Gemini Embedding 2: Our first natively multimodal embedding model\" video-title=\"Gemini 2 multimodal embeddings\" style=\"display: block; height: 416.359px;\">\n        <div class=\"uni-video-player\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;overflow:hidden;direction:ltr;height:416.359px;\">\n         <video crossorigin=\"anonymous\" preload=\"metadata\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"Gemini 2 multimodal embeddings\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/gemini-2-multimodal-embeddings.mp4#t=0.001\" class=\" uni-video-player__video uni-video-player__video--autoplay \" title=\"Gemini 2 multimodal embeddings\" autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" poster=\"https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/models-and-research/gemini-models/gemini-embedding-2/\" style=\"vertical-align: initial; display: inline-block; width: 726px; min-height: 0px;\"></video>\n        </div>\n       </uni-video-player>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini Embedding 2: Our first natively multimodal embedding model&quot;\n         }\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 36px; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\">\n      <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px auto;max-width:726px;\">\n       <div class=\"rich-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.625;\">\n        <p data-block-key=\"6sfyc\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">Like our previous embedding models, Gemini Embedding 2 incorporates Matryoshka Representation Learning (MRL), a technique that “nests” information by dynamically scaling down dimensions. This enables flexible output dimensions scaling down from the default 3072 so developers can balance performance and storage costs. We recommend using 3072, 1536, 768 dimensions for highest quality.</p>\n        <p data-block-key=\"haa1\" style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">To see these embeddings in action, try out our lightweight multimodal semantic search&nbsp;<a href=\"https://findmemedia.lmm.ai/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background: transparent; color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\">demo</a>.</p>\n        <h2 data-block-key=\"8bavo\" style=\"padding:24px 0px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.25px;font-size:36px;line-height:44px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;overflow-wrap:break-word;margin-right:initial;margin-left:initial;font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;hyphens:none;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">State-of-the-art performance</span></h2>\n        <p data-block-key=\"bv6rg\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">Gemini Embedding 2 doesn't just improve on legacy models. It establishes a new performance standard for multimodal depth, introducing strong speech capabilities and outperforming leading models in text, image, and video tasks. This measurable improvement and unique multimodal coverage give developers exactly what they need for their diverse embedding needs.</p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini Embedding 2: Our first natively multimodal embedding model&quot;}\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:726px;margin-inline:auto;margin-block-end:80px;\">\n      <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \" style=\"border-radius:8px;padding:0px;margin:0px;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:726px;margin-inline:auto;height:auto;\">\n       <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;width:726px;height:419.625px;\">\n        <img alt=\"Gemini embedding 2 benchmarks\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260311053350_gemini-embedding-2-benchmarks.width-1000.format-webp.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" data-loading=\"{\n            &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/gemini-embedding-2-benchmarks.width-500.format-webp.webp&quot;,\n            &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/gemini-embedding-2-benchmarks.width-1000.format-webp.webp&quot;\n          }\" class=\"lazy-image--no-blur\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; display: inline-block; height: 419.625px; transition: 0.4s ease-in; object-fit: cover; width: 726px; filter: none !important; cursor: zoom-in;\">\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini Embedding 2: Our first natively multimodal embedding model&quot;\n         }\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 36px; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\">\n      <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px auto;max-width:726px;\">\n       <div class=\"rich-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.625;\">\n        <h2 data-block-key=\"6sfyc\" style=\"padding:24px 0px;margin:initial;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.25px;font-size:36px;font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica;line-height:44px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;hyphens:none;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;overflow-wrap:break-word;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Unlocking deeper meaning for data</span></h2>\n        <p data-block-key=\"b7uot\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">Embeddings are the technology that power experiences in many Google products. From RAG where embeddings can play a crucial role in context engineering to large-scale data management and classic search/analysis, some of our early access partners are already using Gemini Embedding 2 to unlock high-value multimodal applications:</p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"article-module ga4-carousel\" data-component=\"uni-image-carousel\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Article Carousel&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini Embedding 2: Our first natively multimodal embedding model&quot;}\" data-component-initialized=\"true\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px auto;max-width:726px;\">\n      <div class=\"article-carousel\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:800px;margin-inline:auto;\">\n       <button class=\"article-carousel__arrow article-carousel__arrow--previous\" data-ga4-analytics-carousel-scroll-click=\"{&quot;toggle_type_direction&quot;: &quot;arrow - left&quot;}\" aria-label=\"Previous item\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1773207181704\" aria-hidden=\"false\" style=\"z-index:1;background-size:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:18px;border-radius:50%;background-repeat:initial;outline:none;transform:translateY(-50%);overflow:visible;top:calc(50% - 45px);border-width:initial;background-image:none;border-style:none;font-language-override:inherit;height:65px;display:flex;border-color:initial;font-style:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;background-position:initial;font-optical-sizing:inherit;font-variant:inherit;appearance:none;background-clip:initial;font-size-adjust:inherit;left:-100px;width:65px;justify-content:center;align-items:center;background-origin:initial;\">\n        <uni-icon-component icon-id=\"mi-keyboard-arrow-right\" style=\"align-items: center; display: inline-flex;\">\n         <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"icon \" role=\"presentation\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\">\n          <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20260310-1630#mi-keyboard-arrow-right\"></use>\n         </svg>\n        </uni-icon-component>\n       </button>\n       <button class=\"article-carousel__arrow article-carousel__arrow--next\" data-ga4-analytics-carousel-scroll-click=\"{&quot;toggle_type_direction&quot;: &quot;arrow - right&quot;}\" aria-label=\"Next item\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1773207181704\" aria-hidden=\"false\" style=\"z-index:1;background-size:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:18px;border-radius:50%;background-repeat:initial;outline:none;transform:translateY(-50%);overflow:visible;top:calc(50% - 45px);border-width:initial;background-image:none;border-style:none;font-language-override:inherit;height:65px;display:flex;border-color:initial;font-style:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;background-position:initial;right:-100px;font-optical-sizing:inherit;font-variant:inherit;appearance:none;background-clip:initial;font-size-adjust:inherit;width:65px;justify-content:center;align-items:center;background-origin:initial;\">\n        <uni-icon-component icon-id=\"mi-keyboard-arrow-right\" style=\"align-items: center; display: inline-flex;\">\n         <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"icon \" role=\"presentation\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\">\n          <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20260310-1630#mi-keyboard-arrow-right\"></use>\n         </svg>\n        </uni-icon-component>\n       </button>\n       <div class=\"article-carousel__slider\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"false\" id=\"carousel-item-1773207181704\" data-slider-height-loaded=\"true\" style=\"cursor:grab;padding:0px;margin:0px;z-index:1;overflow:hidden;width:726px;transition:left 0.2s ease-out;height:416.375px;\">\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__slide article-carousel__slide--active\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" id=\"carousel-item-1773207181704-0\" aria-label=\"1 of 3\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:800px;left:0px;width:726px;opacity:1;list-style:none;transition:0.2s ease-out;\">\n         <figure style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n          <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;aspect-ratio:16 / 9;width:726px;min-height:auto;\">\n           <img sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 32px), (min-width: 768px and max-width: 1024px) 800px, 565px\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"article-carousel__img\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260311053350_Quote1.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 800w, https://image.jido.dev/20260311053350_Quote1.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 1600w\" alt=\"&quot;We chose Gemini embeddings to help legal professionals find critical information during the discovery process in litigation -- a highly technical challenge in a high-stakes setting, and one Gemini excels at. In our most recent tests, Gemini's multi-modal embedding model improves precision and recall across millions of records, while unlocking powerful new search functionality for images and videos. For legal professionals, these new capabilities open up entirely novel ways to quickly understand case materials in even the largest matters.&quot; Max Christoff, CTO at Everlaw\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260311053350_Quote1.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; display: inline-block; height: 408.375px; object-fit: contain; width: 726px; cursor: zoom-in;\">\n          </div>\n          <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\" style=\"hyphens: manual; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); margin-top: 8px;\"></figcaption>\n         </figure>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__slide\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" id=\"carousel-item-1773207181704-1\" aria-label=\"2 of 3\" inert=\"true\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:800px;left:726px;width:726px;opacity:1;list-style:none;transition:0.2s ease-out;\">\n         <figure style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n          <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;aspect-ratio:16 / 9;width:726px;min-height:auto;\"></div>\n          <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\" style=\"hyphens: manual; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); margin-top: 8px;\"></figcaption>\n         </figure>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__slide\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" id=\"carousel-item-1773207181704-2\" aria-label=\"3 of 3\" inert=\"true\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:800px;left:1452px;width:726px;opacity:1;list-style:none;transition:0.2s ease-out;\">\n         <figure style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n          <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;aspect-ratio:16 / 9;width:726px;min-height:auto;\"></div>\n          <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\" style=\"hyphens: manual; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); margin-top: 8px;\"></figcaption>\n         </figure>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"article-carousel__navigation ga4-bullets\" role=\"tablist\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:36px 0px 0px;z-index:1;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;list-style:none;margin-inline:auto;\">\n        <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button article-carousel__navigation-button--active\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1773207181704-0\" data-index=\"1\" style=\"background-size:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:inherit;border-radius:50%;background-repeat:initial;outline:none;overflow:visible;text-indent:-9999px;background-image:none;border-style:initial;font-language-override:inherit;height:18px;padding:22px;display:block;border-color:initial;font-style:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;background-position:initial;font-optical-sizing:inherit;transition:0.2s ease-in-out;font-variant:inherit;background-clip:initial;font-size-adjust:inherit;width:18px;background-origin:initial;\">Jump to position 1</button>\n        <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1773207181704-1\" data-index=\"2\" style=\"background-size:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:inherit;border-radius:50%;background-repeat:initial;outline:none;overflow:visible;text-indent:-9999px;background-image:none;border-style:initial;font-language-override:inherit;height:18px;padding:22px;display:block;border-color:initial;font-style:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;background-position:initial;font-optical-sizing:inherit;transition:0.2s ease-in-out;font-variant:inherit;background-clip:initial;font-size-adjust:inherit;width:18px;background-origin:initial;\">Jump to position 2</button>\n        <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1773207181704-2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"background-size:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:inherit;border-radius:50%;background-repeat:initial;outline:none;overflow:visible;text-indent:-9999px;background-image:none;border-style:initial;font-language-override:inherit;height:18px;padding:22px;display:block;border-color:initial;font-style:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;background-position:initial;font-optical-sizing:inherit;transition:0.2s ease-in-out;font-variant:inherit;background-clip:initial;font-size-adjust:inherit;width:18px;background-origin:initial;\">Jump to position 3</button>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini Embedding 2: Our first natively multimodal embedding model&quot;\n         }\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 36px; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\">\n      <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px auto;max-width:726px;\">\n       <div class=\"rich-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.625;\">\n        <h2 data-block-key=\"hq4ja\" style=\"padding:24px 0px;margin:initial;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.25px;font-size:36px;font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica;line-height:44px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;hyphens:none;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;overflow-wrap:break-word;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Start building today</span></h2>\n        <p data-block-key=\"20ctg\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">Get started with the Gemini Embedding 2 model through&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/embeddings\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background: transparent; color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\">Gemini API</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.cloud.google.com/vertex-ai/generative-ai/docs/embeddings/get-multimodal-embeddings\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background: transparent; color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\">Vertex AI</a>.</p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <section class=\"code-block\" aria-label=\"Building code\" style=\"margin-block-end: 80px; margin-inline: auto; max-width: 726px;\">\n      <div class=\"code-block__container\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;\">\n       <button aria-label=\"Copy to clipboard\" tooltip=\"Copied\" class=\"code-block__copy-btn\" style=\"display:flex;font-size:inherit;inset-block-start:36px;border-color:rgb(232, 234, 237);font-style:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;right:24px;font-optical-sizing:inherit;transition:background-color 0.1s linear, border 0.1s linear, color 0.1s linear;border-radius:50%;font-variant:inherit;overflow:visible;font-size-adjust:inherit;width:48px;border-width:1px;justify-content:center;align-items:center;font-language-override:inherit;height:48px;\">\n        <uni-icon-component custom-class=\"icon\" icon-id=\"uni-icon-content-copy\" style=\"align-items: center; display: inline-flex;\">\n         <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"icon icon\" role=\"presentation\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\">\n          <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20260310-1630#uni-icon-content-copy\"></use>\n         </svg>\n        </uni-icon-component>\n       </button>\n       <pre aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"code-block__pre kw-speakable-hidden\" style=\"padding:6px;font-size:1em;border-color:rgb(189, 193, 198);min-height:134px;padding-block:36px 24px;overflow-y:auto;font-family:monospace, monospace;margin-top:0px;padding-inline:24px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-block:0px;direction:ltr;\"><code class=\"language-py hljs\" style=\"font-size:16px;overflow-x:auto;font-family:&quot;Roboto mono&quot;, monospace, arial, helvetica;line-height:16px;hyphens:none;overflow-wrap:normal;\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> google <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> genai\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> google.genai <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> types\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"font-style:italic;\"># For Vertex AI:</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"font-style:italic;\"># PROJECT_ID='&lt;add_here&gt;'</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"font-style:italic;\"># client = genai.Client(vertexai=True, project=PROJECT_ID, location='us-central1')</span>\n\nclient = genai.Client()\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">with</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"example.png\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"rb\"</span>) <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">as</span> f:\n    image_bytes = f.read()\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">with</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"sample.mp3\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"rb\"</span>) <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">as</span> f:\n    audio_bytes = f.read()\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"font-style:italic;\"># Embed text, image, and audio </span>\nresult = client.models.embed_content(\n    model=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"gemini-embedding-2-preview\"</span>,\n    contents=[\n        <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"What is the meaning of life?\"</span>,\n        types.Part.from_bytes(\n            data=image_bytes,\n            mime_type=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"image/png\"</span>,\n        ),\n        types.Part.from_bytes(\n            data=audio_bytes,\n            mime_type=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"audio/mpeg\"</span>,\n        ),\n    ],\n)\n\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">print</span>(result.embeddings)</code><button type=\"button\" class=\"bb-copy-btn bb-copy-btn--light\" aria-label=\"复制\" data-state=\"idle\">复制</button></pre>\n      </div>\n     </section>\n     <p data-block-key=\"og3u5\" class=\"drop-cap\"><uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"Gemini 2 multimodal embeddings\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"Gemini 2 multimodal embeddings\" or-mp4-video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/gemini-2-multimodal-embeddings.mp4\" section-header=\"Gemini Embedding 2: Our first natively multimodal embedding model\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" autoplay=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica; font-size: 18px;\"></uni-image-full-width><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica; font-size: 18px;\"></span><uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"Gemini embedding 2 benchmarks\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"Gemini Embedding 2: Our first natively multimodal embedding model\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" autoplay=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica; font-size: 18px;\"></uni-image-full-width><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica; font-size: 18px;\"></span><uni-image-carousel section-header=\"Gemini Embedding 2: Our first natively multimodal embedding model\" images=\"[\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Quote1.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Quote1.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;\\u0022We chose Gemini embeddings to help legal professionals find critical information during the discovery process in litigation \\u002D\\u002D a highly technical challenge in a high\\u002Dstakes setting, and one Gemini excels at. In our most recent tests, Gemini\\u0027s multi\\u002Dmodal embedding model improves precision and recall across millions of records, while unlocking powerful new search functionality for images and videos. For legal professionals, these new capabilities open up entirely novel ways to quickly understand case materials in even the largest matters.\\u0022 Max Christoff, CTO at Everlaw&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Quote2.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Quote2.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;\\u0022Gemini Embedding 2 is the foundation for Sparkonomy’s Creator Economic Equality Engine. Its native multi\\u002Dmodality slashes our latency by up to 70% by removing LLM inference and nearly doubles semantic similarity scores for text\\u002Dimage and text\\u002Dvideo pairs—leaping from 0.4 to 0.8. This powers our proprietary Creator Genome to index millions of minutes of video, alongside images and text, with unprecedented precision—unlocking unbiased brand collaborations and democratizing economic success for every creator.\\u0022 Guneet Singh, Co\\u002Dfounder at Sparkonomy&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Quote3.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Quote3.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;\\u0022The API continuity is excellent. Gemini Embedding 2 drops right into our existing workflow with minimal changes. We’re testing new ways to embed text\\u002Dbased conversational memories together with audio and visual embeddings, especially assistant question\\u002Dand\\u002Danswer pairs, and seeing a 20% lift in top\\u002D1 recall for our personal wellness app.\\u0022  Ertuğrul Çavuşoğlu, Co\\u002Dfounder at Mindlid&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      }\n    \n  ]\" style=\"color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica; font-size: 18px;\"></uni-image-carousel><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica; font-size: 18px;\"></span><uni-code-block data-analytics-module=\"{\n    &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Code Block&quot;,\n    &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini Embedding 2: Our first natively multimodal embedding model&quot;\n  }\" class=\"uni-code-block\" code=\"from google import genai\nfrom google.genai import types\n\n# For Vertex AI:\n# PROJECT_ID='&lt;add_here&gt;'\n# client = genai.Client(vertexai=True, project=PROJECT_ID, location='us-central1')\n\nclient = genai.Client()\n\nwith open(&quot;example.png&quot;, &quot;rb&quot;) as f:\n    image_bytes = f.read()\n\nwith open(&quot;sample.mp3&quot;, &quot;rb&quot;) as f:\n    audio_bytes = f.read()\n\n# Embed text, image, and audio \nresult = client.models.embed_content(\n    model=&quot;gemini-embedding-2-preview&quot;,\n    contents=[\n        &quot;What is the meaning of life?&quot;,\n        types.Part.from_bytes(\n            data=image_bytes,\n            mime_type=&quot;image/png&quot;,\n        ),\n        types.Part.from_bytes(\n            data=audio_bytes,\n            mime_type=&quot;audio/mpeg&quot;,\n        ),\n    ],\n)\n\nprint(result.embeddings)\" description=\"Building code\" lang=\"py\" style=\"color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica; font-size: 18px;\"></uni-code-block><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica; font-size: 18px;\"></span></p>\n     <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini Embedding 2: Our first natively multimodal embedding model&quot;\n         }\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 36px; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\">\n      <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px auto;max-width:726px;\">\n       <div class=\"rich-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.625;\">\n        <p data-block-key=\"27zlq\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">Learn how to use the model in our interactive&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/google-gemini/cookbook/blob/main/quickstarts/Embeddings.ipynb\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background: transparent; color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\">Gemini API</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/generative-ai/tree/main/gemini/embedding/intro_gemini_embedding.ipynb\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background: transparent; color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\">Vertex AI</a>&nbsp;Colab notebooks. You can also use it through&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.langchain.com/oss/python/integrations/text_embedding/google_generative_ai\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background: transparent; color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\">LangChain</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/framework/integrations/embeddings/google_genai/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background: transparent; color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\">LlamaIndex</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://haystack.deepset.ai/integrations/google-genai\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background: transparent; color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\">Haystack</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.weaviate.io/weaviate/model-providers/google\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background: transparent; color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\">Weaviate</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://qdrant.tech/documentation/embeddings/gemini/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background: transparent; color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\">QDrant</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.trychroma.com/integrations/embedding-models/google-gemini\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background: transparent; color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\">ChromaDB</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.cloud.google.com/vertex-ai/docs/vector-search-2/overview\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background: transparent; color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\">Vector Search</a>.</p>\n        <p data-block-key=\"c0len\" style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">By bringing semantic meaning to the diverse data around us, Gemini Embedding 2 provides the essential multimodal foundation for the next era of advanced AI experiences. We can’t wait to see what you build.<span class=\"tombstone\" style=\"background-color: rgb(66, 133, 244); content: &quot;&quot;; display: inline-block; height: 14px; margin-left: 10px; width: 14px;\"></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini Embedding 2: Our first natively multimodal embedding model&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\"></div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Google 推出 Gemini Embedding 2，这是其首个原生多模态嵌入模型，将文本、图像、视频、音频和文档统一到单个语义空间中，用于高级 RAG 和搜索。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google 推出 Gemini Embedding 2，这是其首个原生多模态嵌入模型，将文本、图像、视频、音频和文档统一到单个语义空间中，用于高级 RAG 和搜索。",
  "summary": "Gemini Embedding 2 是 Google 嵌入套件的一次重大升级，从仅限文本的能力转向了完全的多模态架构。它将包括文本、图像、视频、音频和多页文档在内的多种数据类型映射到支持 100 多种语言的统一向量空间中。关键技术特性包括支持交错输入（例如，在一次请求中同时包含图像和文本）以及俄罗斯套娃表示学习（MRL），这允许开发者将输出维度从 3072 缩减到更小的尺寸，以优化存储和性能。该模型旨在通过消除音频转录或独立的模态特定模型等中间步骤，简化 RAG 和语义搜索流水线。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "原生多模态将多种数据类型统一到单个语义嵌入空间中。",
      "explanation": "通过将文本、图像、视频和音频映射到一个向量空间，该模型消除了管理多个专用模型的复杂性，实现了更无缝的跨模态检索和分析。"
    },
    {
      "point": "支持交错输入，捕捉不同媒体类型之间的细微关系。",
      "explanation": "开发者可以在单个请求中传递多种模态，例如图像结合描述性文本。这使得模型能够理解单模态输入经常遗漏的复杂现实世界上下文。"
    },
    {
      "point": "俄罗斯套娃表示学习（MRL）提供了输出维度的灵活缩放。",
      "explanation": "该技术对信息进行“嵌套”，允许开发者将维度从默认的 3072 缩减到 768 或更低。这为平衡搜索准确度与计算及存储成本提供了一个关键机制。"
    },
    {
      "point": "原生音频和文档处理简化了复杂的数据摄取流水线。",
      "explanation": "该模型直接摄取音频而无需文本转录，并可以嵌入多页 PDF。这减少了 AI 应用开发预处理阶段的延迟和潜在的信息损失。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Gemini Embedding 2 将文本、图像、视频、音频和文档映射到单个统一的嵌入空间中，并捕捉超过 100 种语言的语义意图。",
    "该模型原生理解交错输入，因此你可以在单个请求中传递多种模态的输入（例如，图像 + 文本）。",
    "Gemini Embedding 2 结合了俄罗斯套娃表示学习（MRL），这是一种通过动态缩减维度来“嵌套”信息的技术。",
    "它的原生多模态特性通过消除 LLM 推理，将我们的延迟降低了高达 70%，并使语义相似度得分几乎翻倍。"
  ],
